---
description: Ambition doesn't make me ugly. I try to put an end to human perplexity and root for world peace. Because I'm also an artist at war with the world.
author: Nicolas Sursock
pagination:
  data: collections.blog
  size: 9
  reverse: true
eleventyComputed:
  title: Home (Page {{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }})
---

<style>
  [x-cloak] {
    display: none;
  }
</style>
{# This page is built with nunjucks! #}
{# {% set title = 'Home | Cracking Da Code' %} #}
{% extends "layouts/page.njk" %}
{% block head %}
  <link
    rel="preload"
    as="image"
    media="(max-width: 799px)"
    href="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1535903021127-d50417eae4a3?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=480&h=320"/>
  <link rel="preload" href="/static/fonts/aldrich/aldrich-v17-latin-regular.woff2" as="font" crossorigin/>
  <link rel="preload" href="/static/fonts/aldrich/aldrich-v17-latin-regular.woff" as="font" crossorigin/>
  <link rel="preload" href="/static/fonts/aldrich/aldrich-v17-latin-regular.ttf" as="font" crossorigin/>
  <script>
    if (
      localStorage.crdacode_theme === 'dark' ||
      (!('crdacode_theme' in localStorage) && window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)
    ) {
      document
        .documentElement
        .classList
        .add('dark')
    } else {
      document
        .documentElement
        .classList
        .remove('dark')
    }
  </script>
{% endblock %}
