                    <span class=" text-indigo-600 inline">
                      Peace On Earth & End To War
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </template>
                <template x-if="coinFlip >= 0.5">
                  <div>
                    <span class=" text-indigo-600 inline">
                      A Blog For Everyday People
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </template>
              </div>
            </h1>
            <template x-if="!('crdacode_ReturningUser' in localStorage)">
              <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl
                  lg:mx-0">
                In code we trust. I'm a developer and musician working on the sensitive subject of world peace as a side project. That
                time will come, one day you'll see, when we can all be friends.
              </p>
            </template>
            <template x-if="('crdacode_ReturningUser' in localStorage)">
              <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl
                  lg:mx-0">
                We found the code for freedom and in code we trust. We're working on the subject of world peace as a side project. This
                could be heaven for everyone.
              </p>
